{
  "stem": "1581.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were-- the-- the few Jews who were in the army, we were quite popular.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and we didn't really feel any ostracism or-- or elimination.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] life in Czechoslovakia was, as I mentioned before, was almost paradisic.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, it was just what-- what the doctor ordered.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was complete freedom.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were 20 political parties from-- of all denominations, and everything was booming.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a very small Czech nationalist party, negligible.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the-- the vast majority was either Social Democrat or Christian, mostly Catholic.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we had absolute equality in front of the law or in our economic strides.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was-- there were-- you could become whatever you wanted in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Our minister of health was a Jew, for instance.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when I was in the Czech army between '36 and '38, Hitler was in bloom.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, the Nuremberg laws were passed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All the [INAUDIBLE] positions had been eliminated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was in complete control.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He already had occupied the Rhineland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we saw-- we should have seen the writing on the wall.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we felt very secure, because we had-- since World War I, a-- a whole series of military arrangements with England, with France, and with Russia.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And all three of these super powers at that time were obligated to come to our help in case we should be attacked.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We also had-- this was called large entente.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was a small entente consisting of Poland, Yugoslavia, Romania, and Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they too were absolutely obligated by treaty to come to our help.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was a very terrible disappointment when we were sold down the drain at the Munich Conference.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We-- we were mobilized.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
